# darkmap.phasi.space — local/dev environment example.
# Copy to `.env` for local dev (`.env` is gitignored — never commit real keys).
#
# The deployed adapter-node server reads these via SvelteKit `$env/dynamic/private`.

# OpenAQ v3 API key — powers the Smog (PM2.5) overlay + the PM2.5 kernel-diffusion
# → transmission-AOD bridge. Without it the /api/atmospheric/openaq proxy soft-
# degrades (FeatureCollection with `degraded: true`, empty features) and the smog
# overlay renders "unavailable" rather than data. Free key: https://openaq.org
# In production this is provisioned as the `darkmap-secrets` k8s Secret on honey
# (see AGENTS.md "Secrets"), NOT committed here.
OPENAQ_API_KEY=
